com.xekri.leakvm.sdk.spoof.context

Class SpoofPackageManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.pm.PackageManager
      • com.xekri.leakvm.sdk.spoof.context.SpoofPackageManager

  • public class SpoofPackageManager
extends android.content.pm.PackageManager
    SpoofPackageManager is an spoof class to "hack" the userland PackageManager. Is very usable when you like hack MBaaS(Mobile Backend as a Service) and validation systems.
